dotfiles
========

This is my configuration files, aka. 'dotfiles'.


Usage
-----

Check out the repo somewhere and use the ./dotfiles.sh script to manage
dotfile symlinks.

List installed/not installed symlinks:
----
  ./dotfiles.sh list
----

Install symlinks:
----
  ./dotfiles.sh install
----

Remove symlinks:
----
  ./dotfiles.sh remove
----
